andard deviation to describe the variation about the mean. Values in the mi=
ddle near the mean are most likely to occur. It is symmetric and describes =
many natural phenomena such as people=E2=80=99s heights. Examples of variab=
les described by normal distributions include inflation rates and energy pr=
ices. <br></div></div></div><div id=3D"div_block-1207-4013" class=3D"ct-div=
