n: center;">All values have an equal chance of occurring, and the user simp=
ly defines the minimum and maximum because they have no knowledge of which =
values are more likely than others. Examples of variables that could be uni=
formly distributed include manufacturing costs or future sales revenues for=
 a new product. <br></div></div></div><div id=3D"div_block-1222-4013" class=
=3D"ct-div-block box-link white-background"><img id=3D"image-1138-4013" alt=
